cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with the problem of automatic annotation of synaptic connections in 3D electron microscopy data of the Drosophila brain. This involves image segmentation and classification, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.NE, cs.LG). The authors also mention the use of deep learning models (cs.AI) and software development (cs.CL) in their work. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
